  Jaroszynski for testing

*vdk-2.4.1 (29 May 2006)

  29 May 2006; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org>
  -files/vdk-2.0.2-makefile.in.patch, -files/vdk-2.4.0-gcc3.4.patch,
